Name: Sluggy Jean Takes a Hike
About the game: Sluggy Jean Takes a Hike is a game about Sluggy Jean's Journey through 50 unique mazes. They utilize their sticky slug faculties to jump onto walls and find their way through each maze. After enough levels, They challenge the Universe! And after doing so, Sluggy Jean finds themself endeavoring their best to elude through each maze in an endeavor to take down the challenger.
